  "texts": [
    "We aim to address these issues by introducing ILAP, a web-based language assessment platform, where assessments of language proficiency can be created, administered and scored automatically.",
    "The first type of test integrated on the platform is an EIT pipeline.",
    "Automating a language test requires automating several individual components involved in the testing process.",
    "While, to our knowledge, there is no fully automatic pipeline for the EIT developed yet that allows full flexibility, there have been studies on automating individual components of the test, such as item creation (Christensen et al., 2010) or scoring (Graham et al., 2008; Isbell et al., 2023).",
    "The findings of these studies show promising re-sults for the feasibility of automated EITs."
  ],
  "correct_citations": [
